---
// Founders component - Premium SaaS leadership team section
import FancyHeading from './FancyHeading.astro';
---

<section 
  class="founders py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-32 bg-gray-50"
  aria-labelledby="founders"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-16">
    <!-- Section Background Panel -->
    <div class="founders-panel bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16 shadow-sm">
      
      <!-- Top Header -->
      <div class="founders-header text-center mb-12 md:mb-16" data-reveal>
        <FancyHeading 
          as="h2"
          id="founders"
          text="Meet the team behind SafeBox"
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4"
        />
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Trust-first systems, built with real-world operational discipline.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation Pills -->
      <div class="founders-nav flex justify-center gap-3 mb-12 md:mb-16" data-reveal>
        <a 
          href="#zac-bragg"
          class="founder-nav-pill px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium rounded-full border border-gray-300 bg-white text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-50 hover:border-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-900 focus:ring-offset-2 transition-colors"
        >
          Founder
        </a>
        <a 
          href="#lubna-fatima"
          class="founder-nav-pill px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium rounded-full border border-gray-300 bg-white text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-50 hover:border-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-900 focus:ring-offset-2 transition-colors"
        >
          Foundational AI Engineer
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Zac Bragg Profile Block -->
      <article 
        id="zac-bragg"
        class="founder-profile-block bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12 mb-12 md:mb-16 shadow-sm"
        data-reveal-index="0"
      >
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 mb-10">
          <!-- Left Column: Avatar, Name, Role, Location, Chips -->
          <div class="founder-info">
            <div class="founder-avatar mb-6">
              <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-gray-100 border-2 border-gray-200 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700">ZB</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              Zac Bragg
            </h3>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 font-medium mb-1">
              Founder, ClarityPath AI Consulting
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 mb-2">
              Systems Architect, Clarity OS
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
              Rural Tennessee
            </p>
            
            <!-- Value Chips -->
            <div class="founder-chips flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="value-chip px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 text-gray-700">
                Infrastructure first
              </span>
              <span class="value-chip px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 text-gray-700">
                Trust-centered
              </span>
              <span class="value-chip px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium rounded-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 text-gray-700">
                Field proven
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right Column: Bio -->
          <div class="founder-bio space-y-4">
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Zac Bragg is the Founder of ClarityPath AI Consulting and the systems architect behind Clarity OS.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Over a 20+ year career at AT&T, Zac rose from frontline sales to regional leadership, leading large-scale technology modernization and deployment programs across thousands of retail locations. Operating out of AT&T's Atlanta headquarters, he worked at the intersection of executive strategy and frontline execution, translating complex enterprise initiatives into systems that functioned reliably in the field.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              His work included leading region enterprise-wide Salesforce and Microsoft Teams deployments supporting hundreds of locations and cross-functional teams.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              That experience shaped his approach to AI: infrastructure first, execution over theory.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              At ClarityPath, Zac helps small and mid-sized operators, SaaS builders, and growth-stage companies implement AI and technical systems in ways that are practical, secure, and operationally sustainable. Clarity OS is designed as a privacy-forward, trust-centered system that reduces operational chaos instead of adding to it.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Zac currently lives in rural Tennessee, where he prioritizes family, community, and building digitally at his desk or hands on in his workshop. He builds companies the same way he builds systems: deliberately, ethically, and for the long term.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mini Cards Grid -->
        <div class="founder-mini-cards grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-10">
          <!-- Mini Card 1: Credentials and Experience -->
          <div class="founder-mini-card bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6" data-reveal-index="1">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              Credentials and Experience
            </h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 font-medium">
              Enterprise Leadership
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
                <span>20+ years at AT&T, Fortune 50</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Led modernization programs across 2,500+ retail locations</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Directed retail automation across 280 stores spanning 10 states</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Orchestrated Salesforce CRM rollout across 400+ stores achieving 90 percent adoption in 6 months</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Launched Microsoft Teams enterprise rollout supporting hundreds of locations and regional leadership</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Led East Region automated kiosk deployment across approximately 1,200 locations</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Led executive war rooms with 100 percent escalation resolution</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
                <span>AT&T Service Excellence Award recipient for Salesforce deployment leadership</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Two time consecutive AT&T Summit Award winner</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Mini Card 2: Certifications -->
          <div class="founder-mini-card bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6" data-reveal-index="2">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
              Certifications
            </h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-6">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Certified ScrumMaster, CSM</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
                <span>SAFe 6 Agilist</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Scrum Better with Kanban</span>
              </li>
