              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Change Management and Field Readiness</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Cross-Functional and Vendor Leadership</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
